Package io.dazzleduck.sql.flight.server

Class DuckDBFlightSqlProducer

java.lang.Object
io.dazzleduck.sql.flight.server.DuckDBFlightSqlProducer
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimpleBulkIngestConsumer, SqlProducerMBean, AutoCloseable, org.apache.arrow.flight.FlightProducer, org.apache.arrow.flight.sql.FlightSqlProducer
public class DuckDBFlightSqlProducer extends Object implements org.apache.arrow.flight.sql.FlightSqlProducer, AutoCloseable, SimpleBulkIngestConsumer, SqlProducerMBean
It's a simple implementation which support most of the construct for reading as well as bulk writing to parquet file. For now only property which is supported is database, schema and fetch size which are supplied as the connection parameter and available in the header. More options will be supported in the future version. Future implementation note for statement we check if its SET or RESET statement and based on that use cookies to set unset the values
